%description
user-space wrapper library for the pipes-and-filters pattern, based on the ACE \
framework (see: http://www.cs.wustl.edu/~schmidt/ACE.html).
In particular, the library lightly encapsulates the ACE_Stream and ACE_Module \
classes, introducing a new set of (control) interfaces to support asynchronous \
operation, and additional concepts, such as 'session' data and messages. \
In conjunction with additional, modular data processing functionality \
(see e.g.: https://github.com/esohns/libACENetwork), this approach facilitates \
the separation of data processing from application-specific logic and therefore \
enables portable approaches to (distributed) application design

